A strategic game themed after hacking, and a clone of Lego's Spybotics: The
Nightfall Incident. Uses PyGame for visuals, and the Enum python class
(easy_install[-2.7] enum). Released under the SmartPL, see LICENSE file. NOT
PLAYABLE YET!

Future features:
30% - AI for enemy programs
 0% - Check for whether any program occupies node.
 0% - Network map for going between nodes (aka levels)
 0% - Credit system after winning each level
 0% - Shop for buying more programs

Special thanks to:
Brian Kent        for making and releasing the Visitor font as freeware.
PyGame developers for making such a great library!